➜北京野生动物园回应游客坐车顶游览：系小朋友随机行为
http://www.sohu.com/a/419842697_260616	26812
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
showVrsPlayer({
bid:'215631423',
width: '500',
height: '375',
autoplay: false,
